---
title:  BBQ Chicken Includes recyclable aluminum tray
description: Get ready for an American classic--BBQ chicken and all the fixins! Chicken cutlets slathered in BBQ sauce bake beside seasoned sliced potatoes showered with cheddar in our oven-ready tray (no pans to clean!). While the oven does the work, you'll toss the slaw. Juicy BBQ chicken plus golden brown cheesy taters and creamy, tangy slaw--it's summer on a plate all year!
